<p><b>CLEAN YOUR CLOSETS FOR ST VINCENT DE PAUL</b>.
On Saturday, April 23 (5:00-7:00pm) and Sunday,
April 24 (7:30am-7:00pm), an SVdP truck will be in
the O’Dea parking lot, where our Cathedral
Vincentians will accept your gently used clothes,
household goods and other items. After we “Stuff the
Truck,” SVdP will resell your donated items
through local SVdP thrift stores, with proceeds used to
support SVdP activities throughout King County, all of which benefit our 
neighbors in need. Donations are tax deductible. <i>Information</i>, event chair Larry Beyer, 206-234-7438.</p>
