Kent and Renton. A donation of $150 is suggested. RSVP by April 22 to
<a href="mailto:donnaw@svdpseattle.org?subject=Blue Dress Breakfast">Donna 
Whitford</a>, 206-767-9975 (ext 1132).</p>

